messages.msg: Welcome to our site! If you are looking for prayer or someone to chat with, reply to this message or email us at prayer@fightlust.com
Welcome to FightLust.com! How can we support you in your journey towards healing today?
Gone threw alot of healing just feeling alone
I'm sorry to hear that you're feeling alone. We're here to offer support and encouragement. Would you like to share a prayer request or talk about how you're feeling?
I understand your concern. I'm here to provide support and assistance. If you'd prefer to speak with a human agent, I can help with that. Would you like me to escalate the conversation?

We understand that sometimes you need to talk to a real person for prayer, guidance, or encouragement. We are here to support you. Please hold as we connect you with a ministry team member who can assist you in your journey.
